---
layout: layouts/_base.njk
---

<div class="bg-golden-fizz">
  <div class="fixed" style="top: 33%;">nav</div>
  <div
    class="relative grid min-h-screen"
    style="
      grid-template-columns: repeat(12, [gutter] 2rem [column] 1fr) [gutter] 2rem;
      grid-template-rows: auto 1fr auto auto 1fr auto;
    "
  >
    <a
      class="block mt-4 mb-8"
      style="grid-column: column 1 / gutter 10; grid-row: 1 / span 1;"
      href="/"
      ><img
        style="width: calc(566 * var(--fluid-bp));"
        src="/images/logos/logo.svg"
    /></a>
    <!-- prettier-ignore-line -->
    {% set concepts = ["Data as Labour / Data Dignity (DaL/DD)", "Quadratic
    Voting (QV)", "Radical Antitrust", "Intersectional Social Data (ISD)",
    "Quadratic, Financing (QF)", "COST / SALSA"] %}
    <!-- prettier-ignore-line -->
    {% set columnRow = [[1, 3],[4, 3],[7, 3],[1, 4],[4, 4],[7, 4]] %}
    <!-- prettier-ignore-line -->
    {% for concept in concepts%}
    <!-- prettier-ignore-line -->
    {% set column = columnRow[loop.index0][0] %}
    <!-- prettier-ignore-line -->
    {% set row = columnRow[loop.index0][1] %}
    <a
      class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8"
      style="
        grid-column: column {{ column }} / gutter {{ column + 3 }} ;
        grid-row: {{ row }} / span 1;
      "
      href="#"
    >
      <img
        class="w-full mb-4"
        style="max-width: 256px;"
        src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,"
      />
      <h2 class="text-size-1 text-center">{{ concept }}</h2>
    </a>
    <!-- prettier-ignore-line -->
    {% endfor %}
    <div
      id="socialMovementMarquee"
      class="sticky bottom-0 pt-2 leading-none bg-white overflow-hidden"
      style="grid-column: gutter 1 / column 10; grid-row: 6 / span 1;"
    >
      <span class="font-display text-size-5 uppercase mx-6 whitespace-no-wrap"
        >A Social Movement for Next-Generation Political Economies</span
      >
    </div>
    <aside
      class="text-white bg-black"
      style="grid-column: column 10 / -1; grid-row: 1 / -1;"
    >
      <a class="block m-4" href="#">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-size-1">
          Distribute Emergence<br />GitxChange2: Quadratic Funding Hackathon
        </h2>
        <p class="text-size-1">October 5 - November 1, 2020</p>
      </a>
      <hr class="m-4" />
      <div class="mt-4 mx-4 overflow-y-hidden">
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold">E. Glen Weyl</p>
          <p>(twitter) Aug 2, 2020</p>
          <p>
            I gave it a cold? I gave it a virus. A computer virus. God creates
            dinosaurs. God destroys dinosaurs. God creates Man. Man destroys
            God. Man creates Dinosaurs. Forget the fat lady! You're obsessed
            with the fat lady! Drive us out of here! Do you have any idea how
            long it takes those cups to decompose.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</div>
